      <title>沙特阿美石油贸易商因奖金问题在休斯顿举行罢工</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-02/aramco-oil-traders-stage-walkout-in-houston-amid-bonus-dispute</link>
